div.div: Official 4-koma manga adaptation based on the anime series written by mato and serialized in Shounen Jump+. It features chibi versions of the characters and retells the story in a caricaturing way. Note: For every episode of DARLING in the FRANXX, there are 3 chapters/pages illustrating the events of the episode, with the exception of the final episode, which had 4 chapters.
Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu - Anthology side: Roxy
Anthology manga focusing on Roxy Migurdia from Mushoku Tensei.
